reviewText: Good item it is great to see & hear stars I have grown up with in a relaxed place listening to songs & stories.
Not what I expected the artists did mostly talking about road stories
My husband and I like this program and now we can watch when every we want and nothing better on TV
I love this dvd. This one continues the legacy of the first one. I had enjoyment and laughs galore. I am going to whatch this over again. The shipment was prompt and in great condition.
THE BEST.  IF YOU LIKE THE FAMILY REUNION VIDEOS, YOU WILL LOVE THIS ONE!!  YOU WILL BE VERY HAPPY WITH THIS ONE.

The Country Family Reunion 2 was great. All the dvds from CFR are well worth the price of the dvd. We have watched it over and over again, and wish they would put out more at a lesser price so those of us who are senior citizens could afford to buy them. I would reccomend this dvd to anyone. It was great.

Listening to and seeing some of country music's greats perform is a definite treat.  I've watched this DVD many times already and it's like a family
reunion each time I do.  These were the folks who played their heart and soul out for us through the 50's, 60's and70's - and thankfully many of them
are still with us today.  Country music WAS music way back then - and this DVD has some of the best of the true country stars on it.
